<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Bagless Fighter Foundation</title>
<style>
body{
    background:#111;
    color:white;
    text-align:center;
    font-family:Arial,sans-serif;
    padding:20px;
}
.container{
    max-width:700px;
    margin:auto;
}
h1{
    font-size:40px;
    color:#ff4747;
}
.tagline{
    font-size:22px;
    margin-bottom:20px;
}
img{
    width:300px;
    border-radius:20px;
}
.progress{
    width:100%;
    background:#333;
    border-radius:20px;
    margin:20px 0;
}
.progress-bar{
    width:0%;
    background:#ff4747;
    padding:15px;
    border-radius:20px;
}
button{
    background:#ff4747;
    color:white;
    padding:15px 30px;
    border:none;
    border-radius:10px;
    font-size:18px;
    cursor:pointer;
}
button:hover{
    background:#ff2222;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <h1>🥊 Bagless Fighter Foundation</h1>
    <p class="tagline">Help Me Beat Air Instead of Walls</p>

    <p>
        A fighter without a punching bag is like a warrior without armor.<br>
        Right now I’m shadowboxing my dreams and punching invisible enemies.<br><br>
        Goal: ₹15,000
    </p>

    <div class="progress">
        <div class="progress-bar">₹0 / ₹15,000</div>
    </div>

    <h2>Scan & Support</h2>
    <img src="your-qr.jpg" alt="Donation QR">

    <br><br>
    <button onclick="alert('Scan the QR and support the mission!')">
        Buy Me a Punching Bag
    </button>
</div>
</body>
</html>
